theorem univ_P1_P2_P3 {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] :
    Topology.P1 (Set.univ : Set X) ∧
      Topology.P2 (Set.univ : Set X) ∧
        Topology.P3 (Set.univ : Set X) := by
  constructor
  · dsimp [Topology.P1]; simp
  · constructor
    · dsimp [Topology.P2]; simp
    · dsimp [Topology.P3]; simp
